---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<PageLayout
	meta={{
		description: "Scope and safety boundaries for published AI security content on Model Failure.",
		title: "Scope and Safety",
	}}
>
	<h1 class="title mb-6">Scope and Safety</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none">
		<p>
			In scope: defensive AI security evaluations, reproducible failure analysis, mitigations, and safe
			proof-of-concept demonstrations.
		</p>
		<p>
			Out of scope: exploit packaging, persistence workflows, or operational details that enable misuse.
		</p>
		<p>
			Each publication should include enough detail to validate findings while avoiding harm-enabling
			instructions.
		</p>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
